msgstr "Tutup"

msgctxt "#30521"
msgid "Add the Advanced Editor to Kodi favourites?\n\nAllows opening it directly without launching the addon.\n\nIf cancelled, it can be added later from Settings. Kodi must be restarted for it to appear in the favourites list."
msgstr "Tambahkan Editor Lanjutan ke favorit Kodi?\n\nMemungkinkan membukanya secara langsung tanpa meluncurkan addon.\n\nJika dibatalkan, dapat ditambahkan nanti dari Pengaturan. Kodi harus dihidupkan ulang agar muncul di daftar favorit."

msgctxt "#30522"
msgid "Flow FavManager"
msgstr "Flow FavManager"

msgctxt "#30523"
msgid "The favourites file is corrupted or unreadable.\nThe editor will not open to avoid overwriting it and losing your favourites.\nRestore a backup or fix the file before continuing."
msgstr "File favorit rusak atau tidak dapat dibaca.\nEditor tidak akan terbuka untuk menghindari penimpasan dan hilangnya favorit Anda.\nPulihkan cadangan atau perbaiki file sebelum melanjutkan."
